Class HttpClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.security.access.httpclient.HttpClient

  • public class HttpClient
extends java.lang.Object
    Implementation of a HTTP Client. Relies on com.tivoli.am.fim.soap.client implementation of HttpClient.
